
This fix keeps the contents of Entry-boxes, Drop-Down-Menus etc visible when using dark GTK themes.

This is the fix from DeLorean Dark theme so thanks to them.

Copy userContent.css to "~/.mozilla/firefox/userprofile/chrome/" where userprofile=numbersandletters.default

Example: /home/mona/.mozilla/firefox/mwad0hks.default/chrome/

If "chrome" folder is not present just create it.
